headline: Trident Appoints Jim Haney as Chief Financial Officer to Support Next Phase of Growth
summary: FAIRFAX, Va., September 25, 2025--Trident Solutions ("Trident"), a rapidly scaling, multi-domain defense electronics platform backed by ATL Partners, today announced the appointment of Jim Haney as Chief Financial Officer.
